'''水野良'''（{{lang-ja|みずの りょう}}，{{bd|1963年|7月13日|catIdx=Ryo, Mizuno}}），本名'''榎本武士'''（{{lang-ja|えのもと たけし}}），因作品《[[罗德斯岛战记|罗德斯岛战记]]》和《[[魔法战士李维|魔法战士李维]]》而知名的[[日本|日本]][[奇幻小说|奇幻小说]]家和[[游戏设计师|游戏设计师]]。出生于[[大阪府|大阪府]]，毕业于[[立命馆大学|立命馆大学]]法学部。<ref name="LedouxRanney1997">{{cite book|last1=Ledoux|first1=Trish|last2=Ranney|first2=Doug|last3=Patten|first3=Fred|title=The complete anime guide: Japanese animation film directory & resource guide|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=WPgiAQAAIAAJ|accessdate=5 July 2011|date=April 1997|publisher=Tiger Mountain Press|isbn=978-0-9649542-5-0|page=140}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2011-01-24/lodoss-online-game-global-rights-licensed-by-gameon|title=Lodoss Online Game's Global Rights Licensed by GameOn|date=24 January 2011|work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|accessdate=5 July 2011|archive-date=2019-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190525210843/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2011-01-24/lodoss-online-game-global-rights-licensed-by-gameon|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="CampDavis2007">{{cite book|last1=Camp|first1=Brian|last2=Davis|first2=Julie|title=Anime Classics Zettai!: 100 Must-See Japanese Animation Masterpieces|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=aHgWAQAAIAAJ|accessdate=5 July 2011|date=2007-08-01|publisher=Stone Bridge Press|page=304}}</ref>

